{"id": 1638, "genre": 1000, "title": "你都腻烦哪些用滥了的游戏设定？", "description": "连圈钱都没啥新点子，要不要偷懒到这种地步！（题图来自：Zbigniew Rogalski）", "record_count": 23848, "comment_count": 52, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201704191341527ksj9ZQJfHcmr1y0.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-04-23T17:00:44Z", "questions": [{"id": 2178, "title": "你都腻烦哪些用滥了的游戏设定？", "content": "你都腻烦哪些用滥了的游戏设定？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 194267, "content": "塔防游戏每个关卡达到三星才能解锁新地图，同一关玩好几遍", "image": "img/option/option/20170419160345ar2IjNLkGWvOc3Zs.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 194268, "content": "有些低幼游戏分享到社交网络才能解锁关卡，打是打不过的", "image": "img/option/option/20170419160649nKi9chsVWAlHjkzg.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 194269, "content": "棋牌类，你永远可以从各种地方拿到金币继续玩", "image": "img/option/option/201704191607402A6UofQ5PTgLn0p9.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 194270, "content": "武侠/仙侠游戏的红白玫瑰双女主设定，一文静一活泼，但都爱你爱的要死", "image": "img/option/option/20170419160903kCRewULuvfVp58zT.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 194280, "content": "AVG游戏，花钱才能买存档点，免费的只有很少，根本不够用", "image": "img/option/option/20170419161613gzq7mEshaAIpcZtx.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 194282, "content": "RPG游戏里白痴一样对话，回复只能对立二选一", "image": "img/option/option/20170419162253fUeirgXH21DW5lKI.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 194283, "content": "主机游戏里用恶心人的 QTE 来卡玩家", "image": "img/option/option/20170419162401ZsnGmYw8lBKCiS7b.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 194286, "content": "NPC 话多，不想听一个套路的悲情故事我只想安安静静砍人", "image": "img/option/option/20170419162438TpFU5iz8OgowG7In.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 194288, "content": "奖杯成就系统，多玩几遍给你一个屁用没有的勋章/成就", "image": "img/option/option/201704191625523Xy0fruVQGWM45hZ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 194290, "content": "签到领奖，打游戏搞得跟上班一样，每天还打卡", "image": "img/option/option/20170419163540zPa3iMmch9Q6s5GI.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 194292, "content": "抽卡，把游戏活活搞成福利彩票", "image": "img/option/option/20170419163742fDs2oURby9aq40Op.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}